<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>축구 선수 명단</title>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="client.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <style>
        .team-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .team {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .red-box {
            background-color: red;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px;
            display: inline-block; /* 한 줄에 여러 박스가 나열되도록 설정 */
        }
        .green-box {
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px;
            display: inline-block; /* 한 줄에 여러 박스가 나열되도록 설정 */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>축구 선수 명단</h1>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="players" class="form-label">선수 이름을 입력하세요</label>
        <textarea id="players" name="players" rows="10" class="form-control"
                  placeholder="각 선수 이름을 줄바꿈으로 구분하세요"></textarea>
        <small class="form-text text-muted">예: 홍길동, 김철수, 이영희</small>
    </div>

    <button id='submitBtn' class="btn btn-primary">명단 제출</button>

    <div class="team-container">
        <div class="team" id="redTeam">
            <h3>빨간 팀</h3>
            <div id="redPlayersContainer"></div> <!-- 빨간 팀 선수들을 표시할 컨테이너 -->
        </div>
        <div class="team" id="greenTeam">
            <h3>초록 팀</h3>
            <div id="greenPlayersContainer"></div> <!-- 초록 팀 선수들을 표시할 컨테이너 -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
